				<li>Communication plan including an organisation chart (who will be responsible for what at a high level)</li> <!-- template to come <%= link_to 'Initiation', page_path('projmgtinitiation'),class: 'center' %>-->
				<li>An initial risk assessment</li> <!-- template to come <%= link_to 'Initiation', page_path('projmgtinitiation'),class: 'center' %>-->
				<li>Any other considerations documented like vendor involvement, contact issues.</li> <!-- template to come <%= link_to 'Initiation', page_path('projmgtinitiation'),class: 'center' %>-->
				<li>A Quality Plan</li>
